# Brett Stark About Me - Project Context

## Project Overview
Professional about me page for Brett Stark - static HTML/CSS site deployed on Vercel.

## Tech Stack
- HTML5 with semantic markup
- CSS3 with custom properties (CSS variables)
- Google Fonts (Inter)
- Vercel for hosting
- Plausible for analytics

## Development Commands
```bash
npm run dev          # Start Vercel dev server
npm run deploy       # Deploy to production
git add . && git commit -m "message" && git push  # Standard git workflow
```

## File Structure
```
public/
├── index.html       # Main page content
├── styles.css       # All styling with responsive design
├── og-image.png     # Social media preview
└── favicon.ico      # Site icon
```

## Code Standards
- Clean, semantic HTML
- CSS custom properties for theming
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Accessibility features (skip links, focus states)
- SEO optimized meta tags

## Common Tasks
- Update URLs when changing domains (canonical, og:url only - images are relative)
- Test responsive design across breakpoints
- Verify analytics and SEO meta tags
- Maintain consistent styling with existing design system

## Notes
- Site uses relative URLs for images to avoid domain change issues
- Dark mode support via CSS `prefers-color-scheme`
- All styling in single CSS file for simplicity
- Optimized for Core Web Vitals